(739, '0764548476', 'Java, XML, and Web Services Bible', NULL, 'This title provides a comprehensive reference/tutorial for Java programmers who want to tap the synergy of XML and Java in key Web development tasks. The Java, XML, and Web Services Bible serves as a reference/tutorial for a variety of XML and Java related topics. It covers areas such as B2B, Instant Messaging, Java and XML Binding, Scalable Vector Graphics, and Application development with XML and JSP. It discusses some commercial and open technologies used with Java and XML such as Cocoon, Batik, and Xerces.', '2002-01-29', 950, 'http://books.google.fr/books/content?id=-Tt1QgAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', 'http://books.google.fr/books?id=-Tt1QgAACAAJ&dq=Java&as_pt=BOOKS&hl=&source=gbs_api', 233, '35.40', 1),
