(940, '115987977X', 'Php', 'Système de Publication Pour L\'internet, Drupal, Mediawiki, Prométhée, Typo3, Vbulletin, Phpboost, Joomla!, Moodle, Triade-Educ, Wordpress', 'Les achats comprennent une adhsion l\'essai gratuite au club de livres de l\'diteur, dans lequel vous pouvez choisir parmi plus d\'un million d\'ouvrages, sans frais. Le livre consiste d\'articles Wikipedia sur: Systme de Publication Pour L\'internet, Drupal, Mediawiki, Promthe, Typo3, Vbulletin, Phpboost, Joomla!, Moodle, Triade-Educ, Wordpress, Freedom-Ecm, Copix, Guppy, Apdev, Prestashop, Limesurvey, Cmsimple, Xoops, Phpbb, Egroupware, Jelix, Liste de Frameworks Php, Direct News, Fluxbb, Oscommerce, Zikula, Symfony, Rbs Change, Claroline, Automne Cms, Phplist, Wikkawiki, Dotclear, Peel, Dokuwiki, Phpmyadmin, Cacti, Vtiger Crm, Codeigniter, E-Venement, Gepi, Simple Machines Forum, Wackowiki, Tikiwiki, Piwigo, Magix Cjquery, Portix-Php, Phorum, Phpcompta, Agora, Fire Soft Board, Dokeos, Punbb, Kumbia Php Framework, Postnuke, Php-Gtk, Ovidentia, Simpleweb, Lodel, Npds, Cms Made Simple, Statusnet, Webshare, Cakephp, Yii Framework, Icebb, Thelia, Icare, Magento, Phpmyvisites, Posh, 4images, Woltlab Burning Board, Open Source Developers\' Conference, Havefnubb, Zend Framework, Plici, Gul2.0, Contactform, Wamp, Phenix, Phpsysinfo, Textpattern, Bbclone, Hoa Framework, Akroweb Developper, Prado, Mambo, Silverstripe, Phalanger, Phpgedview, Pmwiki, Invision Power Board, Mybulletinboard, Gd, Association Franaise Des Utilisateurs de Php, Andi Gutmans, Pdomap, Simplexml, Wikini, Agavi, Serendipity, Crawltrack, Pear, Mesdiscussions.net, Ming, Piwik, Phpgroupware, Rportal, Geeklog, Apimo, Roundcube, Selfbuild, Ldapsaisie, E107, Phpwiki, Paamayim Nekudotayim, Horde, Smarty, Php Data Objects, Internet Messaging Program, Bitweaver, Phpthumb, Blog: cms, Nocc, Gcp Community, Zend Engine, Phpunit, Aceboard, Tigerwiki, Wikiwig, Agora-Project, B2evolution, Pocket Hph, Pwsphp, Licence Php, Portailphp, Bbpress, Alternativ