(983, '0071461515', 'Teach Yourself PHP With MYSOL', NULL, 'An easy-to-follow guide for new users of PHP with MYSQL This book will help you start writing HTML pages using the programming language PHP—even though you’re just beginning. Comprehensive but concise, it focuses on techniques will give you the building blocks to create more dynamic Web sites. This easy-to-use guide provides the necessary tools for building an easy-to-maintain, open source website and adding interactivity and other features.', '2005-10-26', 224, 'http://books.google.fr/books/content?id=ADkXAAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', 'http://books.google.fr/books?id=ADkXAAAACAAJ&dq=PHP&as_pt=BOOKS&hl=&source=gbs_api', 304, '51.50', 1),
